title: Honeymoon for everyone (1941) 43 MINUTES OF NOTHING BUT LAFFS!

sources.title: Honeymoon for everyone (1941) 43 MINUTES OF NOTHING BUT LAFFS!
sources.description:
A peanut vendor listens to Sam's story of trying to fix a troubled couple's marriage during his honeymoon. After locking them in a room to reconcile, the couple falls in love. Sam's intervention leads to disaster, and in the end, he decides to mind his own business â€” but not before a narrow escape from death.
